node.text:
⭐️WIN A £500 CAMPTOO VOUCHER, SUP SURFING PACKAGE AND LOCK M OUT SECURITY DEVICE⭐️

We’ve teamed up with Lock M Out and Sup Zoom for the perfect giveaway! There's a chance to win a £500 Camptoo rental voucher, Sup Surfing Package and Lock M Out Security Devices!🔒🏄‍♂️

For your chance to win, you must:

1. Follow @camptoo @supzoomglobal and @lockmout on Instagram
2. Tag a friend (more tags means more entries so get tagging all your friends!)
3. Share this post to your story!

We’d also love to see your best camping photos and videos.
DM us if you’d like a chance to feature on our socials!📸

The competition ends at midnight on 26th July 2021!🌟

The winner will be announced on the 2nd August and contacted by DM. Good luck!🏆
** You must be aged 23 or older to rent a Camptoo van **
*must be U.K. resident

🇬🇷👙WIN A 7-NIGHT ALL INCLUSIVE HOLIDAY TO GREECE FOR TWO & A @lookfantastic SUMMER BEAUTY BUNDLE🇬🇷👙

GIVEAWAY TIME🥳… Spend 7 Nights soaking up the sun at one of Kos’ most stylish resorts, the ultramodern @michelangeloresortspa😍 We’ve teamed up with our friends at @lookfantastic to treat one of our followers to a luxury holiday on the pretty beachfront AND a beauty bundle to achieve that all time summer glow💋🏝

To be in with a chance of winning👑👇
- Like this post
- Tag the person you would take
- Both Follow @trendingtravel.co.uk , @lookfantastic & @michelangeloresortspa
-Share this post to your story

Pssst… each new tag is an additional entry🤫👀

The lucky winner will receive their beauty bundle worth £1500 of Look Fantastic goodies and a 7-night stay at @michelangeloresortspa, all Inclusive with flights and transfers🤩✨

The competition closes at 23:59 26/07/21⏱

Please be aware of fake accounts trying to contact you during the competition. This is our only official page and the winner will be announced via our story on 27th July 2021. T&C’s will be available at trendingtravel.co.uk/competition
